msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Kung nasa labas ka ng US, inirerekomenda naming NOWPayments (pinakababang "
"bayarin, direkta sa iyong wallet). Kung nasa US ka, Stripe Crypto ay isa "
"ring opsyon. Maaari mong i-activate ang maraming serbisyo at hayaan ang "
"iyong mga bisita na pumili!"

